metadata.name: DIAMOND
metadata.description:
I was inspired to create this picture by the work of a talented New York photographer QUIL LEMONS

The size of the original canvas is 40 by 40 inches of 100 linen

The work is inlaid with SWAROVSKI crystals jewelry is made of silver potal

Then the canvas was scanned with a resolution of 15,000 x 15,000 px, 900 dpi

after that, it is animated, sound is added and visualized
